  "subject": "Fixed distribution of k8s Helm Artifact",
  "commit_message": "Fixed distribution of k8s Helm Artifact\n\nCloud Technology Artifacts before were belonging\nto each vf module. Now they are only on the list of\nCliud Archive artifacts. In coinsequence, in order\nto do the mapping of CTA to vf-module we need to\nlook in the overall artifacts list. The algorithm\nis the same so nothing should be changed except the\nlist we search in.\n\nIssue-ID: SDC-2972\nSigned-off-by: Lukasz Rajewski <lukasz.rajewski@orange.com>\nChange-Id: I7336b494bfaf0ffb7992cf779391abaf16274b5b\n",
